nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kneecap@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kneecap@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kneecap@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">KNEECAP</a>已在2025年的Eden Sessions宣布，并将得到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-streets">Streets</a>的<a href="/artists/mike-skinner">Mike Skinner</a>的支持。查看下面的详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/kneecap-03-06-2024-3761722">Kneecap：给和平，抗议和聚会一个机会</a></strong></li></ul><p>爱尔兰嘻哈三重奏将使他们的巨大现场表演登上今年的伊甸夏季会议，并于7月4日演出。</p><p>有了该场景，成员MóglaíBap，Mo Chara和DjPróvaí将在康沃尔郡播放他们的首个现场表演，并将与Streets的Mike Skinner一起加入，他们将提供DJ套装。</p><p>这一消息是随着乐队在过去两年中不断发展的力量 - 以其巨大的首张专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kneecap-fine-art-album-review-3765120">Fine Art</a> ”赢得了粉丝，并分享了广受好评的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/kneecap-film-review-biopic-michael-fassbender-3779661">传记片</a>，使他们看到了NAB <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kneecap-director-dedicates-bafta-to-everyone-who-should-have-their-homeland-respected-3838475">BAFTA的提名</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-2025-kneecap-film-shortlisted-for-best-international-feature-and-best-original-song-3823222">两个奥斯卡奖</a>。</p><p>它也随之而来的是，他们冲进了世界上最大的一些阶段，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2025">格拉斯顿伯里</a>，吉米·法伦的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kneecap-make-explosive-us-tv-debut-on-jimmy-fallon-3599087"><em>《今晚秀》</em></a>以及英国，爱尔兰， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kneecap-announce-fall-2025-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3832896">美国</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-the-feral-scenes-from-kneecaps-massive-free-federation-square-gig-in-melbourne-3845516">澳大利亚的</a>无数<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kneecap-add-extra-london-show-to-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-due-to-phenomenal-demand-3778908">标题表演</a>。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">所有的康沃尔头……</p><p>我们将于7月4日在<a href="https://twitter.com/TheEdenSessions?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@theedensessions @theedensessions</a>担任传奇<a href="https://twitter.com/mikeskinnerltd?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@mikeskinnerltd</a>担任特别嘉宾<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/26ab.png" alt="⚫" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/26aa.png" alt="⚪" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f39f.png" alt="🎟" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />周四下午2.30 <a href="https://t.co/4IdUGdLK2V">https://t.co/4idugdlk2v</a> <a href="https://t.co/FYWpLrFYf2">pic.twitter.com/fywplrfyf2</a>发售门票</p><p>- <a href="https://twitter.com/KNEECAPCEOL/status/1904503749197910246?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年3月25日，</a> Kneecap（@kneecapceol） </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>伊甸会议董事总经理丽塔·兄弟（Rita Broe）宣布增加了2025年的法案，他说：“肯尼卡普（Kneecap）是目前世界上最受关注的行为之一。他们的现场表演是一种自然界的力量 - 不受欢迎，不可预测且完全令人振奋。</p><p>对于Skinner来说，DJ套装是在他十年前首次落后于甲板之后的，并且近年来在英国和欧洲进行了他的个人现场表演，展示了高能量的污垢和车库的融合。</p><p> <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Feden-sessions-tickets%2Fartist%2F31235" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处的</a>2025年伊甸会议的门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/biffy-clyro-add-a-second-date-to-uk-summer-shows-at-2025-eden-sessions-buy-tickets-3842298">比菲·克莱罗（Biffy Clyro）也将在今年的伊甸园会议上排队，他将在2025年的活动中进行两晚演出</a>，来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nova-twins">Nova Twins</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/texas">德克萨斯州</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gary-barlow">Gary Barlow</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-script">剧本</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/deftones">Deftones</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madness">Madness的</a>支持。</p><p>除了在康沃尔郡的演出外，Kneecap还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kneecap-announce-massive-dublin-3arena-gig-to-cap-off-2025-3831725">在都柏林举行的大型竞技场音乐会上四处逛逛2025年</a>。三人组还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kneecap-announce-their-biggest-ever-live-show-at-dublins-fairview-park-3807174">在今年夏天在城市的Fairview Park上演奏他们的“有史以来最大的现场表演”</a> 。 </p><p><iframe title="在格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）2024年对Fontaines D.C.，Lewis Capaldi和Paul Mescal的热爱" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pZLsId29Ba8?start=36&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>三人节的节日露面包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kneecap-wet-leg-underworld-tv-on-the-radio-announced-for-green-man-2025-3841849">在绿人</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-for-people-add-sex-pistols-guns-n-roses-biffy-clyro-kneecap-and-more-to-line-up-3826911">摇滚人</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/flow-festival-2025-charli-xcx-fontaines-dc-khruangbin-beth-gibbons-lineup-3819212">流动节</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-queens-of-the-stone-age-girl-in-red-fontaines-dc-added-to-oya-2025-3819094">Øya</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/50-cent-biffy-clyro-and-snow-patrol-head-eye-catching-trnsmt-2025-festival-line-up-tickets-3818465">trnsmt</a>等停下来。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fartist%2F941396" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处的</a>所有即将到来的英国约会的门票，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fkneecap-tickets%2Fartist%2F2661733" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>获得国际门票。</p><p>在其他Kneecap新闻中，三人<a href="https://www.nme.com/new